metrics_conclusion: In terms of chords and melody, Phantom Hourglass- Inside A House is significantly more complex than the typical song, having above average scores in Chord Complexity, Melodic Complexity, Chord-Melody Tension, Chord Progression Novelty and Chord-Bass Melody.
key_conclusion:
Phantom Hourglass- Inside A House is written in the key of C Major.
